{"comments":"Diffusion Kernels — GPU Compute Kernel ADTs\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nKernels are pure data representing GPU operations. The runtime interprets\nthese kernels to execute actual GPU compute. This separation enables:\n- Serialization and hashing for distributed caching\n- Deterministic replay across systems\n- Algebraic composition of pipelines\n\n## Kernel Types\n\n- EncodeKernel: VAE encode (image -> latent)\n- DecodeKernel: VAE decode (latent -> image)\n- DenoiseKernel: Single denoising step\n- NoiseScheduleKernel: Generate sigma schedule\n- LatentBlendKernel: Blend latents for inpainting\n- CFGKernel: Classifier-free guidance\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Diffusion","Kernels"],"EncodeKernel"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[121,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Diffusion/Kernels.purs","start":[121,3]},"title":"KernelEncode"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Diffusion","Kernels"],"DecodeKernel"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[122,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Diffusion/Kernels.purs","start":[122,3]},"title":"KernelDecode"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Diffusion","Kernels"],"DenoiseKernel"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[123,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Diffusion/Kernels.purs","start":[123,3]},"title":"KernelDenoise"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","Diffusion","Kernels"],"NoiseScheduleKernel"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[124,24],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Diffusion/Kernels.purs","start":[124,3]},"title":"KernelNoiseSchedule"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annota